languages.text: "Благодарю Вашу Светлость за помощь. Я уж думал, что сгину в пасти выродка, как Джиневри, но Император рассудил иначе".
"I thank Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship} for the timely assistance. I thought it was my fate to go down an aberration's gullet, like poor Jinevri, but the Emperor had other plans for me."

languages.text: 「なんとタイミングの良い。ご協力感謝します。かわいそうなジネヴリのように、忌まわしきものののど行きが私の運命だと思っていましたが、皇帝には別のプランがあったのですね」
languages.original_text: "I thank Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship} for the timely assistance. I thought it was my fate to go down an aberration's gullet, like poor Jinevri, but the Emperor had other plans for me."

languages.text: “感谢您的及时支援，大人。我本以为我会像可怜的杰尼娃一样，死在那些怪物手里，但看来帝皇对我另有安排。”
languages.original_text: "I thank Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship} for the timely assistance. I thought it was my fate to go down an aberration's gullet, like poor Jinevri, but the Emperor had other plans for me."

languages.text: "Ich danke Eurer {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft} für die Unterstützung in der Not. Ich dachte, es sei mein Schicksal, im Schlund einer Abscheulichkeit zu enden, wie die arme Jinevri, doch der Imperator hatte anderes mit mir vor."
languages.original_text: "I thank Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship} for the timely assistance. I thought it was my fate to go down an aberration's gullet, like poor Jinevri, but the Emperor had other plans for me."

languages.text: « Merci pour votre aide, Votre Seigneurie. Vous êtes {mf|arrivé|arrivée} à point nommé. J'ai vraiment cru que j'allais me faire avaler tout cru par une aberration, comme cette pauvre Jinevri, mais l'Empereur n'en avait apparemment pas fini avec moi. »
